{"tid":783323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老真係咩都做得出，放工時間就咪死出街啦","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T13:10:37.000Z","uid":33312,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2aabb422089c9b43f6de9cfc0fa7c54147de7462","tid":783323,"uid":33312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係灣仔返工<br />\n放工通常會去橋底坐巴士，坐上層無批鬥座同靜<br />\n<br />\n今日收工我照常去等巴士<br />\n去到企係個廢老後面 大約等兩架車我就上到<br />\n點知等左十幾分鐘都未有車<br />\n前面個廢老就黎料<br />\n開始係到發癲 亂咁指住空氣黎鬧<br />\n又屌人老母 又咒人不得好死<br />\n講埋一大輪聽唔明既野<br />\n點知廢老前面既人慢慢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多陣有車到 廢老上到車係到搵八達通<br />\n我當然唔會等佢啦 我拍完卡9秒9衝去上層<br />\n最後一個位比我坐咗 廢老上到黎又係到發癲<br />\n跟住有人讓左個位比佢 佢即刻坐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我尾站落車 屌佢個廢老一有位坐就正常番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"a465e6f54b2c9d9a54928e7780b499248ad1a48c","tid":783323,"uid":33312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =廢老長命百歲，百病纏身</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7a23bf7ad03eb56beda36030e9dd4a732ae6d81","tid":783323,"uid":33312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a71023230414f1fda32b4a9be9ab91699b6ef00","tid":783323,"uid":33312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"推到多D人睇到，下次唔好比廢老扮癲嚇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}